<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device- width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Recertification Inquiry</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
        .email-container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; padding: 30px 40px; }
        .greeting { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
        .message { font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .highlight { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .signature { margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #dddddd; }
        .signature .name { font-weight: bold; font-size: 15px; color: #333333; }
        .signature .title { font-size: 13px; color: #666666; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .signature .contact { font-size: 13px; color: #333333; }
        .signature .contact a { color: #00aaff; text-decoration: none; }
        .signature .company { color: #dc000d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; }
        .signature .motto { font-size: 11px; color: #88ff88; font-style: italic; margin-top: 8px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <p class="greeting">Hi,</p>
        
        <p class="message">I've reached out a few times and haven't heard back, which usually just means the timing isn't right.</p>
        
        <p class="message">That's completely fine. I'd rather know than keep checking in when it isn't the right moment.</p>
        
        <p class="message">If you're still thinking about it, just reply, happy to answer questions or pick up where we left off. If not, let me know and I'll close the file for now.</p>
        
        <p class="message">One thing worth keeping in mind: the recertification deadline for {{Property Address}} doesn't move. The earlier this gets started, the more options you have.</p>
        
        <p class="message">Either way, thank you for your time.</p>
        
        <p class="message">Best,</p>
        
        <div class="signature">
            <p class="name">Genesis Torrealba</p>
            <p class="title">Sales & Operations Coordinator</p>
            <p class="contact">
                <a href="mailto:gt@engsv. com">gt@engsv. com</a> | <strong>Direct:</strong> 954-951-1482<br>
                <span class="company">Engineering Services, Inc.</span><br>
                Office: 954-951-2121 | <a href="https://engsv. com/recertification">engsv. com</a>
            </p>
            <p class="motto">Committed engineering. Seamless compliance.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>